description: A survivor is pulled from the rubble in the port city of Izmir as the quake's death toll rises to 64.
title: Turkey earthquake: Search efforts continue for third day as death toll rises
title_page: Turkey earthquake: Search efforts continue for third day as death toll rises - BBC News
maintext: "It was a really strong shaker almost enough to knock you off your feet. Running out of the house with my children was like a drunken wobble," Chris Bedford, a retired British teacher who lives in Urla, west of Izmir, told the BBC.
